title: New: Teebs – Bleep
content:
Teebs is back with another slice of LA to distract us from the long UK winter we’re all so readily getting stuck into.

It’s drastically more restrained than his LP, remarkably less tactile and well, it’s only 1.17 in length. To be quite honest it’s not even very good, but it’s Teebs, so I’ll take what I can get.
author: 5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d24
